<p dir=3D"auto">State is a Python dictionary. It consists of observation <c=
ode>state['obs']</code>, legal actions <code>state['legal_actions']</code>,=
 raw observation <code>state['raw_obs']</code> and raw legal actions <code>=
state['raw_legal_actions']</code>.</p>
